# nexus /.ext — external resource SSOT (raw-format DSL)
# Inherits hive/.raw raw#14 ext-ssot whitelist (kind ∈ {ssh, api, service, binary, submodule, pod})
# Format spec: hexa-lang self/raw_loader.hexa
#
# nexus 가 직접 의존하는 외부 자원만 등재. super-bundle 레벨 (`/core/.workspace`) 의
# member exports/imports 와 중복되더라도 nexus 의 도구가 직접 호출하는 entry 는 여기 명시.
# READ-ONLY data deps (atlas.n6 등) 는 .own atlas-absorb-mandatory 와 cross-link.

ext 1 live "hexa-lang CLI — script runtime for tool/*.hexa"
  slug hexa-cli
  kind binary
  subkind cli
  path /Users/ghost/core/hexa-lang/hexa
  version >=0.1.0-stage1
  use kick_dispatch.hexa, witness_emit.hexa, atlas_absorb_*.hexa, drill_*.hexa 모두 hexa runtime 위에서 실행. 직접 CLI 호출 (`hexa <script.hexa>`) 만 canonical.
  why nexus 의 모든 governance + ω-cycle 도구가 hexa-lang. raw#9 hexa-only.
  proof hexa --version
  alive static

ext 2 live "n6 atlas main — 1.5MB consolidated lens registry"
  slug atlas-n6
  kind submodule
  subkind data_n6
  canonical /Users/ghost/core/n6-architecture/atlas/atlas.n6
  symlink   n6/atlas.n6
  owner     n6-architecture
  follower  nexus
  use absorb target — `.own` atlas-absorb-mandatory 가 모든 ω-cycle witness 를 atlas.n6 + atlas.append.<slug>.n6 에 흡수
  why n6-architecture 가 owner. nexus 는 follower, 직접 수정 금지 (READ + APPEND only via witness_emit).
  proof test -L /Users/ghost/core/nexus/n6/atlas.n6 && test -f /Users/ghost/core/nexus/n6/atlas.n6
  alive static

ext 3 live "n6 atlas signals — 4205 signal lenses"
  slug atlas-signals-n6
  kind submodule
  subkind data_n6
  canonical /Users/ghost/core/n6-architecture/atlas/atlas.signals.n6
  symlink   n6/atlas.signals.n6
  owner     n6-architecture
  follower  nexus
  use signal-lens 검색 + drill seed 도출. .guide convention: NEVER edit (READ-ONLY).
  why n6-architecture canonical. nexus 가 수정하면 atlas drift 즉시 발생.
  proof test -L /Users/ghost/core/nexus/n6/atlas.signals.n6
  alive static

ext 4 live "ssh host ubu1 — kick backend GPU compute (RTX 5070 12GB, driver 580.126.09)"
  slug ssh-ubu1
  kind ssh
  addr ubu
  user aiden
  remote-home /home/aiden
  hexa-path /home/aiden/.hx/bin/hexa
  use kick backend dispatch (claude_code / codex_cli / gemini_cli on remote), GPU compute offload, anima cell-learning GPU smoke
  why /core/.workspace host.ubu1 참조. parity-verified 2026-04-22 (FULLCHIP_RESET 해소).
  proof ssh -o ConnectTimeout=8 -o BatchMode=yes ubu true
  alive cron-probe

ext 5 live "ssh host ubu2 — kick backend GPU compute (RTX 5070 12GB, open-driver 580.126.09)"
  slug ssh-ubu2
  kind ssh
  addr ubu2
  user summer
  remote-home /home/summer
  use kick backend dispatch, sister-host to ubu1, 2-way GPU parity
  why /core/.workspace host.ubu2 참조. RTX 50-Blackwell open-kernel-modules 필수 (closed=RmInitAdapter fail).
  proof ssh -o ConnectTimeout=8 -o BatchMode=yes ubu2 true
  alive cron-probe

ext 6 live "ssh host htz — kick backend CPU compute (Ryzen 9 7950X3D 32T, 124GB RAM)"
  slug ssh-htz
  kind ssh
  config /Users/ghost/core/nexus/config/hetzner.json
  cpu-only true
  use CPU-bound kick backend, high-memory tasks (Mac 24GB jetsam-prone path 우회)
  why discrete GPU 없음 (lspci 2026-04-22 확정). iGPU=AMD Raphael, /dev/kfd 있지만 CUDA 없음.
  proof test -f /Users/ghost/core/nexus/config/hetzner.json
  alive cron-probe

ext 7 retired "anthropic API direct route — RETIRED 2026-04-27 (raw 71 + R4 cli-only migration)"
  slug api-anthropic
  kind api
  retired-date 2026-04-27
  retired-reason user directive 2026-04-27 "Anthropic API 관련 남아있어 — cli only — Claude Code CLI 호출은 hive CLI 이용". Direct API + ANTHROPIC_API_KEY env auth retired. SOLE credential path = Mac OAuth slot pool (~/.claude-claude<N>/) accessed via Claude Code CLI through hive's custom-provider-claude-cli extension.
  replacement /Users/ghost/core/hive/packages/coding-agent/src/core/hive-cli-router.ts (TS) + ext 8 hive-coding-agent (binary)
  convergence /Users/ghost/core/nexus/convergence/r4_cli_only_migration_2026_04_27.convergence
  why direct Anthropic API route caused ubu1 sub-agent x-api-key invalid failures (2026-04-27 user-reported). cli-only routing makes Mac OAuth slot pool the SSOT credential path. raw 1 lock applied to hive-cli-router.ts.
  alive never

ext 8 live "hive coding-agent — kick backend dispatch shim"
  slug hive-coding-agent
  kind binary
  subkind cli
  path /Users/ghost/core/hive/packages/coding-agent/dist/cli.js
  use kick run claude_code 백엔드는 hive coding-agent 로 자동 dispatch (raw 44 subagent_dispatch contract)
  why hive 가 coding-agent runtime owner. nexus 는 LLM dispatch 를 hive 에 위임.
  proof test -f /Users/ghost/core/hive/packages/coding-agent/dist/cli.js
  alive static

ext 9 planned "β QRNG source — ANU multi-stream batch (length=1024)"
  slug qrng-anu-batch
  kind api-endpoint
  endpoint https://qrng.anu.edu.au/API/jsonI.php?length=1024&type=uint8
  throughput-bit-per-sec 8192
  rate-limit 1 req/sec (free tier)
  access public-api
  cost free
  prereq none — 무료 API, HTTP curl + jq, 즉시 가능
  use β channel multi-byte queue feed (1024 byte / 1 req → 1024 cycle 재사용 → effective 1024× throughput vs current length=1)
  why first-kick A2 가 정량한 "8 bit/sec" hard ceiling 은 API parameter 한계 — same endpoint length=1024 면 8192 bit/sec free.
  proof curl -s --max-time 5 'https://qrng.anu.edu.au/API/jsonI.php?length=1024&type=uint8' | jq '.success and (.data|length)==1024'
  alive on-demand
  ramp-phase Tier-1 (immediate, 1-line patch in tool/noise_envelope.hexa:165)
  raw47-channel realization-channel: spec-correction-in-canonical-artifact + tool-edit-and-commit

